Initializes all elements of a range with their $(D .init)
value. Assumes that the range does not currently contain meaningful
content.

Example:
----
struct S { ... }
S[] s = (cast(S*) malloc(5 * S.sizeof))[0 .. 5];
initializeAll(s);
assert(s == [ 0, 0, 0, 0, 0 ]);
----

